beer.beer_description:
For our next seasonal release of our Avalanche Hazy IPA series, our brewers chased down hops from the Land of the Long White Cloud. 

New Zealand hops Motueka, Wai-iti and Riwaka are the stars of this release, giving it distinctive melon and tropical characters with a herbaceous twist. 

As with every Avalanche release, the hops are front and centre, and supported by meticulous use of malts to give the beer moderate bitterness and a full body.
